Grounded turned to Nightlight.  "This is the pod.  I am going to open 
it, you two be prepared."  Grounded walked up to the pod, felt it out 
until finally finding the control.  He opened his arm then inserted a 
connetcting cable to the pod.  He stood for a couple seconds then 
detached. "It should open now."
